casebody.data:
Wednesday, May 26, 1999

MOTION DOCKET

99-682. State ex rel. Hall v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 98AP-130. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. It appearing to the court that the record in this case was filed on April 29, 1999, but the receipt of the record inadvertently was not docketed until May 25,1999,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that appellant’s brief shall be due within forty days of the date oí this entry, and the parties shall otherwise proceed in accordance with the Rules of Practice.
